main

Class Tape

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Tape

  • public class Tape
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Brainfuck machine. Unlike the classical representation of Brainfuck language in which the machine is limited to 30,000 cells, this implementation includes the machine with tape, dynamically extensible in both directions. Each cell's size is 1 byte.
